iTask - A Minimal To-Do App

🚀 Overview

iTask is a simple and efficient to-do app built with React 19, Vite, and Tailwind CSS. This project follows modern best practices and ensures a smooth and fast user experience.

🔥 Features

✅ Minimalistic UI - Clean and simple design.

⚡ Lightning Fast - Powered by Vite for optimal performance.

🎨 Styled with Tailwind CSS - Fully responsive and customizable.

🔄 React Hooks - Efficient state management.

🔧 ESLint & Prettier - Clean and maintainable code.

🚀 Easy Deployment - Deployed via GitHub Pages.

🛠 Tech Stack

React 19

Vite

Tailwind CSS

ESLint & Prettier

GitHub Pages (for deployment)

📦 Installation & Setup

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/AhmadFazel786/todo-app.git
cd todo-app

Install dependencies:

npm install

Run the app in development mode:

npm run dev

Open http://localhost:5173 to view it in the browser.

Build for production:

npm run build

Deploy to GitHub Pages:

npm run deploy

